{"id":8183,"date":"2026-03-13T13:52:03","date_gmt":"2026-03-13T06:52:03","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=8183"},"modified":"2026-03-13T13:52:03","modified_gmt":"2026-03-13T06:52:03","slug":"titanium-dioxide-mang-loc-chong-nang-vat-ly","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/titanium-dioxide-mang-loc-chong-nang-vat-ly\/","title":{"rendered":"Titanium Dioxide (TiO\u2082) \u2013 M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd, n\u00e2ng tone t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Titanium Dioxide c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u1eafng c\u1ea3n UVB\/UVA2 t\u1ed1t trong kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd. N\u00f3 th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc Zinc Oxide, l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n trong c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1eady n\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o m\u00e0u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tone-up, makeup body.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gioi-thieu-chung-ve-titanium-dioxide\"><\/span><b>Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u chung v\u1ec1 Titanium Dioxide<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ean khoa h\u1ecdc\/INCI: Titanium Dioxide (TiO\u2082). Thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc kho\u00e1ng\/v\u1eadt l\u00fd.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1ch g\u1ecdi kh\u00e1c: \u201cPhysical filter\u201d, pigment tr\u1eafng (CI 77891) trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m &amp; d\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea9m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c \u2013 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed: \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 trong s\u01a1n, nh\u1ef1a, th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m (m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi TiO\u2082 th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m), d\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea9m b\u00f4i ngo\u00e0i da v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vai tr\u00f2 trong KCN: Che ph\u1ee7 UVB m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n UVA2 (320\u2013340 nm); B\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, d\u1ecbu da, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vai tr\u00f2 trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m: L\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o m\u00e0u, gi\u00fap n\u00e2ng tone da, gi\u00fap da tr\u1eafng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dac-diem-hoat-chat-titanium-dioxide\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t Titanium Dioxide<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat-cua-titanium-dioxide\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Titanium Dioxide<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8184\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8184\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8184 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/91-1.webp\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a titanium dioxide trong kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/91-1.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/91-1-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/91-1-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/91-1-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8184\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a titanium dioxide trong kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i UVB: \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u1edbn cho SPF nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1eafn UVB; b\u1ed5 sung UVA2 \u1edf m\u1ee9c v\u1eeba.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean: \u00edt b\u1ecb suy gi\u1ea3m d\u01b0\u1edbi tia UV so v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u1eefu c\u01a1 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u0169.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng n\u00e2ng tone: h\u1ea1t tr\u1eafng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1\/t\u00e1n x\u1ea1 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, v\u1eeba ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng, \u201cche m\u1edd\u201d l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng\/khuy\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eb9 tr\u00ean body\/face.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u00e1p \u1ee9ng da t\u1ed1t: ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, d\u00f9ng sau th\u1ee7 thu\u1eadt nh\u1eb9, v\u00f9ng quanh m\u1eaft (\u00edt cay).\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c d\u00f2ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd (ZnO, TiO\u2082) th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng sau khi x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n (sau 3-4 ng\u00e0y) v\u00ec da \u0111ang y\u1ebfu t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. C\u00e1c d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 ch\u00e2m ch\u00edch tr\u00ean da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u01b0u \u00fd: Ngay sau x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n ho\u1eb7c t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eabn n\u00ean \u01b0u ti\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p che ch\u1eafn b\u1eb1ng m\u0169, \u00e1o, kh\u1ea9u trang do da \u0111ang c\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i.<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">MUA NGAY: <a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/kem-chong-nang-vat-ly-gsc\/?_gl=1*7tz82m*_up*MQ..*_gs*MQ..&amp;gclid=Cj0KCQiA1czLBhDhARIsAIEc7uhO20WtzLakS_BBYCast0rmxiHqa0_G_IY5AbaiTgJ6lP7j5yJxaRoaAniDEALw_wcB&amp;gbraid=0AAAAA_YZ5LfGYb4T6bYbYh5BZsM_4myxG\">Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh v\u1eadt l\u00fd GSC<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong-cua-titanium-dioxide\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Titanium Dioxide\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>T\u00e1n x\u1ea1 + ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 + h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> TiO\u2082 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u1edbi tia UV r\u1ed3i ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1\/t\u00e1n x\u1ea1; m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n ho\u00e1 th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7t.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc &amp; x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 &amp; an to\u00e0n c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c:<\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>Non-nano (\u2265100 nm):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> che ph\u1ee7 cao \u2192 <\/span><b>white cast<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Nano (~20\u2013100 nm):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> trong su\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9; t\u0103ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong n\u1ec1n c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thuong-co-trong-dang-kcn-nao-ket-hop-toi-uu\"><\/span><b>Th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 trong d\u1ea1ng KCN n\u00e0o &amp; k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1i \u01b0u?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>D\u1ea1ng n\u1ec1n:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> cream\/lotion, gel-cream, stick, tinted; s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m body\/tone-up d\u00f9ng TiO\u2082 r\u1ea5t ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8185\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8185\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8185 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/91-2.webp\" alt=\"TiO\u2082 + ZnO c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i \u201ckinh \u0111i\u1ec3n\u201d trong ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng\u00a0\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/91-2.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/91-2-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/91-2-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/91-2-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8185\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">TiO\u2082 + ZnO c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i \u201ckinh \u0111i\u1ec3n\u201d trong ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">TiO\u2082 + ZnO: TiO\u2082 l\u00e1 ch\u1eafn trong v\u00f9ng UVB\/UVA2 c\u00f2n ZnO ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m trong v\u00f9ng UVA1. T\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng kho\u00e1ng ho\u00e0n ch\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n; kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1eady b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1eb1m \u1edf s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng n\u00e2ng tone, l\u00e0m l\u1edbp trang \u0111i\u1ec3m da nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hybrid (TiO\u2082\/ZnO + h\u1eefu c\u01a1 (Tinosorb S)): c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9, t\u0103ng SPF\/UVA-PF v\u1edbi n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1i \u01b0u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">TiO\u2082 + Iron Oxides (CI 77491\/92\/99): t\u1ea1o s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ed9 tinted, gi\u00fap l\u1edbp finish l\u00e0m da kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u00e1i, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 che \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh (HEV) h\u1eefu \u00edch cho PIH\/n\u00e1m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-su-dung-san-pham-co-titanium-dioxide\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 Titanium Dioxide<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-kcn-co-titanium-dioxide-dung-tot-nhat-khi-nao\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng KCN c\u00f3 Titanium Dioxide d\u00f9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khi n\u00e0o?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sinh ho\u1ea1t h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y, v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng \u2013 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m: TiO\u2082\/ ZnO n\u1ec1n d\u1ecbu, kh\u00f4ng m\u00f9i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi \u2013 th\u1ec3 thao \u2013 b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n: c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng thu\u1ea7n v\u1eadt l\u00fd ho\u1eb7c hybrid; ki\u1ec3m tra kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc (water-resistant) c\u1ee7a s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da sau t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n: Ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng sau t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng, tr\u00e1nh hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng PIH (t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 sau vi\u00eam) l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-chong-chi-dinhkhong-nen-ket-hop-voi-chat-nao-khong\"><\/span><b>C\u00f3 ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh\/kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00e1ng ho\u00e1 h\u1ecdc \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc kh\u00e1c<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>D\u1ea1ng x\u1ecbt\/aerosol: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean d\u00f9ng cho tr\u1ebb em v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 b\u1ec7nh l\u00fd h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p tr\u00e1nh h\u00edt ph\u1ea3i (an to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p); \u01b0u ti\u00ean cream\/lotion\/stick.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>White cast:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u0169 khi\u1ebfn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u00f9ng Titanium Dioxide d\u1ec5 b\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i v\u1ec7t tr\u1eafng, v\u00e2n kem. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 nano, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e3n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 finish \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8187\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8187\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8187 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/91-4.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai\/cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kcn Titanium Dioxide kh\u00f4ng?\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/91-4.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/91-4-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/91-4-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/91-4-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8187\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai\/cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kcn Titanium Dioxide kh\u00f4ng?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3, tuy nhi\u00ean n\u00ean xem k\u1ef9 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p nh\u1eefng m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc n\u00e0o. Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd (TiO\u2082\/ZnO) th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn an to\u00e0n. V\u1eabn c\u1ea7n <\/span><b>thoa \u0111\u1ee7 li\u1ec1u 2 mg\/cm\u00b2<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, d\u1eb7m l\u1ea1i 2\u20133 gi\u1edd khi \u1edf ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u00e1o\/m\u0169\/k\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-thoa-lieu-luong-cho-kem-chong-nang-vat-ly\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch thoa &amp; li\u1ec1u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>Li\u1ec1u chu\u1ea9n:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ~<\/span><b>2 mg\/cm\u00b2<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> (m\u1eb7t + c\u1ed5 ~ 1\/3\u20131\/2 mu\u1ed7ng c\u00e0 ph\u00ea).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u201c\u0111i\u1ec3m \u2013 t\u00e1n \u2013 d\u1eb7m\u201d:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ch\u1ea5m 10\u201312 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u2192 t\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec1u (v\u1ed7, kh\u00f4ng mi\u1ebft ch\u00e0); n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i v\u1ec7t tr\u1eafng chi l\u00e0m hai l\u1edbp m\u1ecfng ho\u1eb7c chuy\u1ec3n sang d\u00f2ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng tinted.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>D\u1eb7m l\u1ea1i:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> m\u1ed7i <\/span><b>2\u20133 gi\u1edd<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi; sau b\u01a1i\/\u0111\u1ed5 m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i\/kh\u0103n lau.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Layer v\u1edbi make-up: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m l\u1edbp l\u00f3t n\u00e2ng tone ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n lu\u00f4n v\u00ec finish \u0111\u1eb9p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u tham kh\u1ea3o<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Campaign for Safe Cosmetics. (n.d.). Titanium Dioxide. Safe Cosmetics.<a href=\"https:\/\/www.safecosmetics.org\/chemicals\/titanium-dioxide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> https:\/\/www.safecosmetics.org\/chemicals\/titanium-dioxide\/<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\/31588611\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Dr\u00e9no B, Alexis A, Chuberre B, Marinovich M. Safety of titanium dioxide nanoparticles in cosmetics. J Eur Acad Dermatol Venereol. 2019 Nov;33 Suppl 7:34-46. doi: 10.1111\/jdv.15943. PMID: 31588611.<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Titanium Dioxide (TiO\u2082) \u2013 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc kho\u00e1ng UVB\/UVA2 B\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, n\u00e2ng tone t\u1ed1t, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m &amp; s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m body.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":8188,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-8183","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8183","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=8183"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8183\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":9278,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8183\/revisions\/9278"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/8188"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=8183"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=8183"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=8183"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}